个人简介
			
			Dr.WeilinSun
Professor,InstituteofPolymerScience,
CollegeofMaterialsScienceandChemicalEngineering,
ZhejiangUniversity,Hangzhou310027China
Email:opl_sunwl@emb.zju.edu.cn
Tel:86-0571-87951059

Professionalactivities:
MemberofChineseChemicalSociety
MemberofChineseChemicalEngineeringSociety

Specialty:
Organicsynthesisandpolymerscience

Education:
WeilinSunbecomeaprofessorinZhejiangUniversityin1999.HewasaPost-doctoralfellowinInstituteofChemistry,ChineseAcademyofSciencein1994-1996,andwasaPh.D.inDepartmentofPolymerScienceofEngineering,ZhejiangUniversityin1994.

Presentresearch：
Hispresentresearchismainlyconcentratedonsynthesisandapplicationofaromaticheterocyclicpolymers,whichincludes:1)preparationandthepropertiesofconductiveandsoftferromagneticpolymers.2)Synthesisandstructuralstudyofnovelpolyamides,polyimidesandpoly-schiffbasecontainingbisthiazolering.

CurrentProjects:
1.Studiesonsoftferromagneticmaterialsofnovelaromaticheterocyclicpolymer.
2.Preparationofsoftferromagneticmaterialsofaromaticheterocyclicpolymerchelatingrareearthsandtheirmagneticmechanism.
			
				
			工作研究领域
			
			Hispresentresearchismainlyconcentratedonsynthesisandapplicationofaromaticheterocyclicpolymers,whichincludes:1)preparationandthepropertiesofconductiveandsoftferromagneticpolymers.2)Synthesisandstructuralstudyofnovelpolyamides,polyimidesandpoly-schiffbasecontainingbisthiazolering.
			
				
